    "body": "the problem is not the block tag - the problem is that the first parameter must be a number in 1.10.6 - it is fixed on master and will be rolled out with 1.10.7 that you can use hex strings here.\r\nCurrently you need to do:\r\n`\r\ncurl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\"method\": \"eth_feeHistory\",\"params\": [4,\"latest\",[]],\"id\": 0}'\r\n`\r\n",
